properties.name: Union/Steve Biko Building
properties.desc: Contains the SRC offices, as well as the counselling centre, The Oppidan Press and Activate. The Oppidan dining hall is in this building, as are the Union Labs which are on the bottom level down the stairs - one can print in colour here.

properties.name: Drama Department
properties.desc: Also the Rhodes Theatre that is used extensively during the National Arts Festival in the June vac.

properties.name: Humanities Office
properties.desc: For any queries about your Humanities degree, or any Humanities subject one can go here for help.

properties.name: Hamilton Building
properties.desc: Also known as the Hamilton Building

properties.name: Journalism Department
properties.desc: As a first year Journ student you can't get in with your student card, but wait for anyone else and they should let you in.

properties.name: Great Hall
properties.desc: Many tests and exams are written here.

properties.name: Biological Sciences Building
properties.desc: Contains Zoology, Entomology, Biotechnology, Biochemisty Microbiology

properties.name: Economics Department
properties.desc: Entrance is from the fountain quad.

properties.name: School of Fine Art
properties.desc: Art Department

properties.name: Linguistics

As this building is new, it is not logged on Google Maps yet.

properties.name: Business School

properties.name: Law Department

properties.name: Counselling Centre
properties.desc:
The Counselling Centre is situated on the top floor of the Bantu Stephen Biko Building in Prince alfred Street, next to the swimming pool.

Counselling services are free of charge, confidential and short term focused to encourage you to address a particular difficulty that you are experiencing at that point in time.

properties.name: Arts Major and Minor

properties.name: Zoo Major and Minor
properties.desc: Lecture theatres upstairs and downstairs in the building

properties.desc: Lecture theatres. Entrance from Artillery Rd.

properties.name: Psych Major/Minor
properties.desc: Lecture theatres

properties.name: Swimming Pool
